\par\pard\plain \tx0\li360\fi360\sa120\sl262\slmult1\ltrch\loch {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf5 Sarah readies Evan for her fundraising event, noticing his nervousness but amazed at how effortlessly he fits into her high-class, charitable sphere. Though clearly an outsider, he wins the crowd's favor. Witnessing Evan flourish in her world eradicates her last shred of hesitation, letting her fully commit her heart to him.<!$Scr_Ps::3><$Scr_Ps::2>}
\par\pard\plain \tx0\sb180\sl264\slmult1\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b1\i0\cf6 Leading Context:<!$Scr_Ps::2><$Scr_Ps::3>}
\par\pard\plain \tx0\li360\fi360\sa120\sl262\slmult1\ltrch\loch {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf5 This scene follows the last scene, where Evan was waiting at the open bar in the grand ballroom, talking to the bartender, Jenni,  while Sarah finished checking that everything was going as planned.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf5 The previous scene ended with Jennie serving Sarah a glass of wine and giving Evan a gentle hug.<!$Scr_Ps::3><$Scr_Ps::2>}
